  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/dabdcad502b88ba05b4f09a09dba6dc0.avif?t=1761317704\" width=107 height=68 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/9eb147ad71e20252f8d0ecc063c82bd3.avif?t=1761317704\" width=162 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/ec37f4d7d80ac57c5205c7b4d9277009.avif?t=1761317704\" width=161 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/1df29baf06cf28e054e0ed3ce1c5bd48.avif?t=1761317704\" width=332 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/dccf0c7ddca5492827a8401d4b281225.webp?t=1761317704\" width=54 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/049116081a92141872d7e274cc64d8fb.webp?t=1761317704\" width=615 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue Conflict is a game that combines the tactical depth of a wargame with the unpredictability of a roguelike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each campaign unfolds differently — maps, units, and upgrades change with every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Units lost are gone forever, and if you fail a campaign you will have to start a new one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/6c82093a1830e337e76df5d125f8fa0c.webp?t=1761317704\" width=616 height=43 /></span><br>At the beginning of each new campaign you are presented with the option to pick one of fifteen unique armies, each with their own strengths and weaknesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the campaign you will also have to opportunity to customize your army by requesting new units and assigning upgrades to them to help further specialize your army. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/9fbe2175d5fa08e294a8d534c881ffd3.webp?t=1761317704\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All the maps in Rogue Conflict are procedurally generated, ensuring that no two runs are the same. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll need to carefully plan your attack at the beginning of each mission and make sure you use the maps terrain features to your advantage in order to complete each combat puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/dccbbc5b685d8152c99466640f0fcf7b.webp?t=1761317704\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficulty in Rogue Conflict is designed to push your tactical skills to their limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When advancing your troops, you will have to do so with care, as your opponent will be ready to punish you for every little misstep along the way, and the roguelike nature of the game means that all decisions are final.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Key Features</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 unique armies, each with its own playstyle and unit composition</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 80 unit upgrades to pick from to help further specialize your army </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally-generated maps for endless replayability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep, tactical and challenging gameplay<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/907c2c772e2784551f9588fba7b87276.poster.avif?t=1761317704\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/907c2c772e2784551f9588fba7b87276.webm?t=1761317704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/907c2c772e2784551f9588fba7b87276.mp4?t=1761317704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/dabdcad502b88ba05b4f09a09dba6dc0.avif?t=1761317704\" width=107 height=68 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/9eb147ad71e20252f8d0ecc063c82bd3.avif?t=1761317704\" width=162 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/ec37f4d7d80ac57c5205c7b4d9277009.avif?t=1761317704\" width=161 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/1df29baf06cf28e054e0ed3ce1c5bd48.avif?t=1761317704\" width=332 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/dccf0c7ddca5492827a8401d4b281225.webp?t=1761317704\" width=54 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/049116081a92141872d7e274cc64d8fb.webp?t=1761317704\" width=615 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue Conflict is a game that combines the tactical depth of a wargame with the unpredictability of a roguelike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each campaign unfolds differently — maps, units, and upgrades change with every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Units lost are gone forever, and if you fail a campaign you will have to start a new one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/6c82093a1830e337e76df5d125f8fa0c.webp?t=1761317704\" width=616 height=43 /></span><br>At the beginning of each new campaign you are presented with the option to pick one of fifteen unique armies, each with their own strengths and weaknesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the campaign you will also have to opportunity to customize your army by requesting new units and assigning upgrades to them to help further specialize your army. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/9fbe2175d5fa08e294a8d534c881ffd3.webp?t=1761317704\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All the maps in Rogue Conflict are procedurally generated, ensuring that no two runs are the same. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll need to carefully plan your attack at the beginning of each mission and make sure you use the maps terrain features to your advantage in order to complete each combat puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/dccbbc5b685d8152c99466640f0fcf7b.webp?t=1761317704\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficulty in Rogue Conflict is designed to push your tactical skills to their limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When advancing your troops, you will have to do so with care, as your opponent will be ready to punish you for every little misstep along the way, and the roguelike nature of the game means that all decisions are final.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Key Features</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 unique armies, each with its own playstyle and unit composition</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 80 unit upgrades to pick from to help further specialize your army </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally-generated maps for endless replayability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep, tactical and challenging gameplay<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/907c2c772e2784551f9588fba7b87276.poster.avif?t=1761317704\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/907c2c772e2784551f9588fba7b87276.webm?t=1761317704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916010/extras/907c2c772e2784551f9588fba7b87276.mp4?t=1761317704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
